sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant FE as Angular
    participant GW as Gateway
    participant BE as Writer BE
    participant DB as Postgres

    FE->>GW: POST /api/writer/conversations with auth
    GW->>DB: INSERT conversation
    DB-->>GW: id
    GW-->>FE: Conversation id
    FE->>GW: POST /apps/writer/api/chat with messages and conversation_id
    GW->>BE: forwards request
    Note over BE: RAG retrieval runs scoped to that conv
    BE-->>FE: SSE stream
    FE->>GW: POST /apps/writer/api/generate-title
    GW->>BE: forwards request
    BE-->>FE: title string
    FE->>GW: PATCH /api/writer/conversations by id title
    GW->>DB: UPDATE title
